OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,FThe First Minister has been accused of
OL,7,F"refusing to acknowledge that there's
OL,8,Fa crisis in our NHS".
OL,10,FBut Eluned Morgan said her government
OL,11,Fdoes have a plan to speed up waiting
OL,12,Ftimes and is backing it up with extra
OL,13,Ffunding.
