OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,FDuring her weekly question session,
OL,7,Fthe First Minister was challenged by
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Conservative leader, Darren
OL,9,FMillar, who referred to a recent
OL,10,Freport by the Royal College of Nursing
OL,11,Fon the number of patients being
OL,12,Ftreated in corridors in Welsh
OL,13,Fhospitals.
OL,15,FAfter a number of questions, Mr Millar
OL,16,Fsaid: "It's very clear to me and
OL,17,Feverybody in this chamber and anybody
OL,18,Fwatching that you are refusing to
OL,19,Facknowledge that there's a crisis in
OL,20,Four NHS.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
