PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F461A1737474826
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,F"Unless you acknowledge that there's a
OL,7,Fcrisis in our NHS, we will never get
OL,8,Fto deal with that crisis and fix the
OL,9,Fproblem.
OL,11,F"Let me quote ... Helen Wiley of the
OL,12,FRoyal College of Nursing (who said)
OL,13,Fthat this care is of such a standard
OL,14,Fthat it's allowing a situation where
OL,15,Fit's more likely that patients will
OL,16,Fdie as a result of it."
OL,18,FHe went on to say that the problem was
OL,19,Fmade worse by a lack of available beds.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@ZpmtD@cpn
