OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,F"Over 500 times in this report, beds
OL,7,Fare cited as a problem - over 500
OL,8,Ftimes.
OL,10,F"They're not my issues. It's the RCN
OL,11,Fthat's claiming that this is a problem.
OL,13,F"And you know, and I know, that the
OL,14,Fnumber of beds in our national health
OL,15,Fservice since 1999, entirely on
OL,16,FLabour's watch, has reduced by over 30
OL,17,Fper cent, while our population has
OL,18,Fincreased by 10%.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
