OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F461A1737474826
OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,F"So it's not me that's misunderstood
OL,7,Fthe issue. It's you. You're failing to
OL,8,Facknowledge the crisis.
OL,10,F"Failing to train and recruit enough
OL,11,Fdoctors and nurses. You've axed beds,
OL,12,Fclosed hospitals, and you've failed to
OL,13,Fbuild the new hospitals you promised.
OL,15,F"So it's clear that, on your watch as
OL,16,Fa Labour government, the NHS is
OL,17,Fbroken. When are you going to move
OL,18,Fover so that we, Welsh Conservatives,
OL,19,Fcan fix it?"
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@LO]
