OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,FIn response, the First Minister said
OL,7,Fthat spending on the NHS has been
OL,8,Fsqueezed because the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment's own funding has been
OL,10,Fsqueezed by Conservative UK
OL,11,FGovernments.
OL,13,FShe said: "Thankfully, now we've had a
OL,14,Fmassive increase as a result of the
OL,15,FLabour government for the first
OL,16,Fsignificant increase when it comes to
OL,17,Fhealth in Wales when it comes to
OL,18,Fcapital expenditure.
OL,26,@uD@KOU
