OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,F"But we're very clear about the plan
OL,7,Fthat we have. We've got a strategic
OL,8,Fplan when it comes to health. It was
OL,9,Fbuilt together with stakeholders, with
OL,10,Fthe public.
OL,12,F"It was built together with experts
OL,13,Fand the RCN were also involved in the
OL,14,Fdevelopment of that plan.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
