OL,3,CFirst Minister accused of 'refusing to
OL,4,Cacknowledge crisis in NHS'
OL,6,F"When it comes to hospital beds, let
OL,7,Fme tell you that we have more beds in
OL,8,FWales per head than they do in
OL,9,FEngland, and that there is a
OL,10,Frecognition that the way forward here
OL,11,Fis to shift to more support in the
OL,12,Fcommunity, to make sure we do more
OL,13,Fprevention work and to ensure we have
OL,14,Fdigital transformation.
OL,16,F"This is exactly what they're thinking
OL,17,Fof doing in England. Actually, we're a
OL,18,Flong way down that journey in Wales,
OL,19,Fand we're going to stick to the path
OL,20,Fthat we've set out."
